Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_constra...gin_end_points(25.10)  timing_constra...gin_end_points(25.10)

Name
       timing_constraint_enable_report_invalid_begin_end_points

Syntax
       timing_constraint_enable_report_invalid_begin_end_points

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Enables  reporting  of  invalid  begin points/end points specified with
       set_false_path or set_multicycle_path constraint.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

